<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.204494>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Map showing the distribution of L. diaguita and the species of the L. darwinii group more close distributed. Black square: L. diaguita. Black circle: L. quilmes. Black triangle: L. espinozai. Black star: L. koslowskyi. Black diamond: L. abaucan. White square: L. albiceps. White circle: L. lavillai. White triangle: L. calchaqui. White star: L. crepuscularis. Arrow indicates the type locality of L. diaguita." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/204494/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

